The,Google,My,Business,API,allows,business,enterprises,to,create,and,edit,locations,for,purposes,of,updating,or,publicizing,their,physical,addresses,The,API,enhances,the,visibility,of,the,location,of,a,business,in,Google,maps,and,search,results,making,it,suitable,for,integration,with,online,advertising,apps,The,RESTful,API,sends,and,parses,request,data,in,HTTP,format,and,returns,responses,in,JSON,format,Version,brings,real,time,push,notification,for,listing,updates